room_title: Escape room "1959 - Jack's Place" by The Escapeopolis Project in Fayetteville (AR)

room_description: Escapeopolis's Precognition Sensors (EPS) are alerting your Anti-Divergence Team to a forthcoming negative event. There is an 89% probability factor the event may place Jack, an Escapeopolis Observer, who is stationed in the United States in 1959, in harm's way. Your mission is clear: Prevent the negative event and protect the Observer.
